INSERT INTO `affiliate_msg` (`id`, `date`, `name`, `msg`, `affiliate_no`, `reply_no`, `subject`, `status`) VALUES
(10, '2018-07-21 16:43:01', 'Happy Zhou', 'Hi i would like to know why affiliate commissions are set to a minimum transfer of $10.00?\r\n', '7181afd', NULL, 'Affiliate Commissions', 'new'),
(11, '2018-07-21 17:12:11', 'Happy Zhou', 'Hi thank you for your inquiry. 1.This helps us to get serious affiliates. 2. It helps us to recobcile our accounts better when we send money in lumpsums with a minimum of $10.00', NULL, '7181afd', 'Affiliate commisions', 'new'),
(24, '2018-09-29 21:21:55', NULL, 'Valued driver, system was undergoing major upgrades for driver alerts.  If you see email/sms written Mr Test/Testing kindly ignore. Thanks for your patience! \r\n', NULL, NULL, 'Driver Alerts Upgrade', 'new'),
(22, '2018-09-24 13:54:08', NULL, 'Get in on it & win yourself a $50 Spar grocery hamper courtesy of Merchant Couriers plus airtime, pizza & tshirts. Go to https://goo.gl/KPhx35 Ends 15 Nov 2018.', NULL, NULL, 'Grocery Hamper Promo1', 'new'),
(23, '2018-09-26 14:49:56', NULL, 'Affiliate! jump into your dashboard share our ads + your affiliate link with individuals & businesses. Earn 10% as they book with us. www.merchantcouriers.co.zw', NULL, NULL, 'Affiliates motivation1', 'new'),
(25, '2018-11-20 15:30:03', NULL, 'Dear transporter. Having secured some contracts for local and intercity freight loads, as a requirement from business partners. To take advantage of this, kindly email copies to merchantcouriers1@gmail.com. Your truck\'s registration book, current licence disk, current 3rd party insurance, transport permit (if available), and fitness certificate of your trucks. This is for  3.5t to 34t trucks. Merchant Couriers Driver Recruitment Team.', NULL, NULL, 'Contract Documents', 'new'),
(28, '2018-12-25 18:43:12', NULL, 'Merchant Couriers wishes you a Merry Christmas & Happy New Year. Thank you for driving with us in 2018. Drive safely and deliver on time. Stay alert for new delivery jobs in 2019!', NULL, NULL, 'Christmas Message and Promo', 'new'),
(27, '2018-12-25 18:18:44', NULL, 'Merchant Couriers wishes you a Merry Christmas & Happy New Year. Thank you our loyal customer in 2018. Book & get 10% off your next delivery until 10 Jan 2019. ', NULL, NULL, 'Christmas Promo Wishes', 'new'),
(29, '2018-12-25 18:56:28', NULL, '<p>Merchant Couriers affiliates team wishes you a Merry Christmas &amp; Happy New Year. Thank you for sharing our business and offers with your friends and colleagues in 2018. Share the opportunity and start earning more referral commissions in 2019. New opportunities to earn coming in the new year!</p>', NULL, NULL, 'Christmas Promo Wishes', 'new'),
(20, '2018-08-07 22:08:49', NULL, '<!-- #######  YAY, I AM THE SOURCE EDITOR! #########-->\r\n<p>Every week at Merchant Couriers and as an affiliate i ask myself what i\'ve have done after joining this program.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>There are a few things that one ought to do in order to make it in their career. A few of them are setting weekly goals, measuring progress on action taken, brainstorming new strategies, reviewing the old ones and adjusting to methods that produce most results.</p>\r\n<p><strong>What have i done this week?</strong></p>\r\n<p>As a Merchant Couriers Affiliate this week one of the things i did through my affiliate portal was to reach out to key businesses that i feel will benefit the most from the services this company is providing.</p>\r\n<p>Just to give you a rough idea. One of the lists included many restaurants&nbsp; across most of Harare. And this was a test sample. I tweaked the original message a bit but left the main link just to make sure new clients sign up on my affiliate refferal. And it worked. Within minutes of sharing new customers signed up.</p>\r\n<p><strong>This was the message i shared:</strong></p>\r\n<p><em>Greetings, Do you constantly get your restaurant, pub, or cafe supplies delivered and need a reliable courier to partner with? Allow us to introduce you to Merchant Couriers. A fast, effective delivery service you can afford to use. *Simply book online in 1minute and we\'l pick it up and deliver it for you!* That\'s why with our new, fast and convenient mobile app, you can now book and have your delivery done by us. New clients are invited to signup for free and try it out. A 10% Discount applies on your first delivery. For signup please visit http://bit.ly/2MYJYmY We Deliver With Speed! For any further inquiries please call/whatsapp on 263772467352 or 263775972428.</em></p>\r\n<p><em>PS: For any special arrangements tailored to your business\' delivery needs You may contact on either of the numbers above and schedule a meeting.</em></p>\r\n<p>This is how you can make the most of this affiliate program, by thinking outside the box. Ask five main questions regarding who could need this exciting technology and service and do a google search or magazine search or newspaper search. Then compile a list and open your portal and share. One simple 20% action can get you 80% results</p>\r\n<p>1.&nbsp;<em>set weekly goals,</em></p>\r\n<p><em>2. measure progress on action taken,</em></p>\r\n<p><em>3. brainstorm new strategies,</em></p>\r\n<p><em>4. review the old ones and</em></p>\r\n<p><em>5. adjust into new methods that produce the most results.</em></p>\r\n<p>I know when you do this consitently you will strike the golden one very soon and earn your 10% income weekly.</p>\r\n<p>Visit your dashboard this week and review yout efforts and apply these five stages above. Rest assured results will show.</p>\r\n<p><em>What have i done this week? And if nothing, why have i not done it?</em></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Happy Advertising</p>\r\n<p>The Merchant Couriers Affiliate Team</p>', NULL, NULL, 'What have i done this week?', 'new'),
(13, '2018-07-23 09:32:05', NULL, '\r\n<p>Some say opportunity only knocks once at one\'s door. But we believe in the God of second chances and this could be one of them. Imagine opportunities that passed you by sometime before. Simply because you did not have enough money or resources you could not take advantage of them. I know here at Merchant Couriers we have come across many of those. And we know how it feels to watch them pass you by.</p>\r\n<p>The reason we designed this affiliate marketing program was to address a few key issues:</p>\r\n<p>1. For individuals to work from their convenient places and still be able to earn.<br />2. For individuals to be able to earn extra income whether they worked fulltime or had other business commitments even those who didn\'t have a job at all.<br />3. To create jobs or businesses in a new jobs market and innovative ways of employment. (if you didnt have a job or business now you have one!)<br />4. To improve the marketing industry by introducing new and innovative ways to recruit brand ambassadors or advertising agents.(The days of walking up and down the streets are soon to be over)<br />5. To give a fulltime income (10%) for affiliates by getting paid each time a customer books with us and pays for their delivery or service. Imagine this, as we rollout new products (you will get paid for those products too through one customer- fyi it has never happened in zimbabwe too ;-) )<br />6. One way to build our company brand awareness and grow customer base, and revenue thus you also get paid adequately for your efforts as we get more business.</p>\r\n<p>We did this not for ourselves only but for you too. So that you can also benefit financially and experientially.</p>\r\n<p>Thats why we encourage you this new week to take advantage of this affiliate program that you signed up for. Allow us to welcome you again and congratulate you for some new and exciting products that you will witness first hand before everyone else. We are soon to invite you to meet whenever we launch something new. And it will be in a venue but also online for those outside! So we consider you brand\'s family now.</p>\r\n<p>For you we want to make it easy and less hutsle. We have created the tools and we will continue to male more for you to make it. All you have to do is share. Use the sharing buttons, for social media, messaging platforms and emails in your account, and using the link in the sharing corner of your account. This is where the money is. We also have banners that you can add to your websites or blogs to bring refferals to your account. And yes everyone you refer is now both our customer and yours too. If individuals dont take advantage of this businesses might jump on it. Dont let them!</p>\r\n<p>Imagine if you got one big client who pays $1000.00 for their deliveries everyweek. You\'ve earned yourself an easy $100.00. And for as long as they do this. You earn too. So whats stopping you?</p>\r\n<p>Take advantage of what we have built for you and share our products and services. Set goals and targets and get to action.</p>\r\n<p>To learn how intricate parts of our system works. In case a refferal inquires from you how to signup or use it. Here\'s how customers book, pay and actually get their deliveries fulfilled. Visit our youtube page, subscribe to it too.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCIOGN-7WPBLb44cGwIxN6ow</p>\r\n<p><br />To your success this week.</p>\r\n<p>Merchant Couriers Affiliates Team</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>PS: One of you just earned $12.00 this week. (we launched this product less than 7days ago.)</p>', NULL, NULL, 'Making The Most Of Opportunity', 'new'),
(14, '2018-07-25 08:42:09', NULL, '<p>Want to save yourself time when sending your parcel or freight today? Think about how convenient it now is to send a parcel, freight or even move houses. Ã°Å¸Â¤â If you\'re at work, at home or you\'ve even travelled. Don\'t worry, you can send us and we\'l pick it up and deliver it for you, on time!</p>\r\n<p><strong>Book Online</strong></p>\r\n<p>Use the merchant couriers delivery app or website for all your inner city deliveries and pickups, freight loads and furniture moving trips. And fast booking platform.</p>\r\n<p>Plus get 10% discount off the full price on your first delivery booking.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Download Our Mobile App</strong></p>\r\n<p>Download the booking app and experience this convenience on the go! With it you can book a delivery in 2minutes. You can generate a quote too and email it to yourself or potential clients, but before doing so here\'s how you can maximise on your network.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Be Generous and Earn Rewards</strong></p>\r\n<p>In the mobile app you can now become an affiliate of Merchant Couriers and share our products and services to friends, family, businesses and your other networks for potentially new clients and earn yourself some extra income weekly. 10% of any successful delivery booking from your refferals. Just share and we do the rest. Sometimes your network is your next income opportunity Ã°Å¸Ëâ°</p>\r\n<p>Thank you for being our customer.</p>\r\n<p>Make the most of it!</p>\r\n<p>Merchant Couriers Customer Service Team</p>', NULL, NULL, 'Make the most of it!', 'new');
